<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.1.8">
<l>kaṟṟilēṉ kalaika ḷaimpulaṉ karutuṅ</l>
<l>karuttuḷē tiruttiṉēṉ maṉattai</l>
<l>peṟṟilē ṉataṉāl pētaiyēṉ naṉmai</l>
<l>perunilat tāruyirk kellām</l>
<l>ceṟṟamē vēṇṭit tiritarvēṉ tavirntēṉ</l>
<l>celkatik kuyyumā ṟeṇṇi</l>
<l>naṟṟuṇai yākap paṟṟiṉē ṉaṭiyēṉ</l>
<l>nārā yaṇāveṉṉum nāmam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I did not study the philosophies; I directed my mind</l>
<l rend="indent">in [worldly] thoughts which think [only] of the five senses.</l>
<l>I did not gain [any] benefit [from this], therefore I am a simpleton.</l>
<l>I wandered aimlessly wishing evil to all precious life of the great world.</l>
<l rend="indent">[Then] I rejected [that].</l>
<l>Determining a way to refuge which saves [me], I, a devotee, cling, as the best</l>
<l rend="indent">aid, to the name which is pronounced, “Nārāyaṇā!”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
